The 'newverbs' LaTeX package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This package allows the definition of \verb variants which add TeX code before and after the verbatim text.
When used together with the 'shortvrb' package it allows the definition of short verbatim characters which use this variants
instead of the normal \verb.

